A more powerful processor, a larger-resolution camera, a stronger chassis or a display that recognizes the power of touch, are in short the advantages of the recently introduced ninth generation iPhones.
The last two also have a negative impact on the dimensions and weights of iPhones 6s and 6s Plus.
The current trend of Apple was that each new generation of iPhone is lighter than the previous generation.
The exception was only the third and fourth generation, whose weight slightly increased compared to previous iPhones.
The two-gram weight difference in the absence of the news was really negligible.
